<c.bg_transparent>you're not going to testify.</c.bg_transparent>

535
00:31:26.135 --> 00:31:29.134 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's a hearing, not a trial.</c.bg_transparent>

536
00:31:29.214 --> 00:31:30.454 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>She has no choice.</c.bg_transparent>

537
00:31:40.131 --> 00:31:41.924 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Sir.</c.bg_transparent>

538
00:31:42.890 --> 00:31:44.450 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Odo's on subspace.</c.bg_transparent>

539
00:31:44.530 --> 00:31:45.729 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's urgent.</c.bg_transparent>

540
00:31:49.908 --> 00:31:50.989 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>I've made some progress.</i></c.bg_transparent>

541
00:31:51.428 --> 00:31:52.308 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Good.</c.bg_transparent>

542
00:31:53.007 --> 00:31:53.628 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Not good.</i></c.bg_transparent>

543
00:31:54.707 --> 00:31:57.269 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Since the transmission</i></c.bg_transparent>
