554
00:32:24.737 --> 00:32:28.244 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-The wife.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>-The wife.</i></c.bg_transparent>

555
00:32:30.016 --> 00:32:33.015 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Curzon Dax and Enina Tandro.</c.bg_transparent>

556
00:32:34.075 --> 00:32:35.125 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Maybe it was innocent.</i></c.bg_transparent>

557
00:32:35.554 --> 00:32:37.936 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Maybe he was just providing</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>a little emotional support</i></c.bg_transparent>

558
00:32:37.936 --> 00:32:39.186 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>during tough times.</i></c.bg_transparent>

559
00:32:39.913 --> 00:32:41.935 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Or maybe they were taking advantage</i></c.bg_transparent>

560
00:32:41.935 --> 00:32:44.135 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>of the General's absence</i></c.bg_transparent>
