00:32:45.311 --> 00:32:46.652 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>If they were having an affair,</i></c.bg_transparent>

562
00:32:46.652 --> 00:32:49.974 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>that translates into a pretty</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>solid motive for murder.</i></c.bg_transparent>

563
00:33:01.298 --> 00:33:02.939 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The conversations were just the beginning.</c.bg_transparent>

564
00:33:02.939 --> 00:33:04.534 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I've also found records of gifts,</c.bg_transparent>

565
00:33:04.925 --> 00:33:07.667 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>of holidays spent at an inn</c.bg_transparent>
