566
00:33:07.805 --> 00:33:09.245 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( sighs ) What purpose does this serve?</c.bg_transparent>

567
00:33:09.718 --> 00:33:11.724 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-It serves the truth.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Oh, the truth.</c.bg_transparent>

568
00:33:11.724 --> 00:33:13.305 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If there's more to this</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>than meets the eye,</c.bg_transparent>

569
00:33:13.305 --> 00:33:14.205 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I hope you'll explain,</c.bg_transparent>

570
00:33:14.205 --> 00:33:17.396 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>because as it stands</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>this will severely hurt Dax's defense.</c.bg_transparent>

571
00:33:21.323 --> 00:33:23.922 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>My husband was not the hero in life</c.bg_transparent>

572
00:33:24.001 --> 00:33:26.441 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>that he was in death, Mr. Odo.</c.bg_transparent>

573
00:33:27.081 --> 00:33:29.200 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>In death, he became a legend</c.bg_transparent>

574
00:33:29.280 --> 00:33:31.200 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>and I became a legend's wife.</c.bg_transparent>

575
00:33:31.817 --> 00:33:33.979 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>There are people who did not</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>even know my husband</c.bg_transparent>

576
00:33:34.056 --> 00:33:35.317 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>who still contact me.</c.bg_transparent>

577
00:33:35.796 --> 00:33:38.578 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Decades after his death,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>they still mourn him.</c.bg_transparent>

578
00:33:39.036 --> 00:33:39.917 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>But you don't.</c.bg_transparent>

579
00:33:40.175 --> 00:33:43.738 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>No, because I knew the man</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>before he became a legend.</c.bg_transparent>

580
00:33:44.474 --> 00:33:46.356 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>But I also know my place in history.</c.bg_transparent>

581
00:33:46.913 --> 00:33:49.895 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>My place is to carry on bravely,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>never to remarry,</c.bg_transparent>

582
00:33:50.332 --> 00:33:53.114 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>to represent my husband at the banquets</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>given in his name.</c.bg_transparent>

583
00:33:53.311 --> 00:33:56.373 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>But never, never to talk</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>about who he really was.</c.bg_transparent>

584
00:33:57.370 --> 00:33:59.452 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Because nobody wants to hear that.</c.bg_transparent>

585
00:34:01.049 --> 00:34:02.390 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>They may have to hear it now.</c.bg_transparent>

586
00:34:04.587 --> 00:34:07.769 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>No matter what is said,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>they will still embrace his memory...</c.bg_transparent>

587
00:34:11.726 --> 00:34:15.249 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>For he was and always will be</c.bg_transparent>

588
00:34:16.966 --> 00:34:19.126 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>the hero who died for his people.</c.bg_transparent>

589
00:34:24.841 --> 00:34:27.803 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>But perhaps it's time</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>for my place in history to change.</c.bg_transparent>

590
00:34:36.434 --> 00:34:38.155 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You've been protecting her reputation.</c.bg_transparent>

591
00:34:38.437 --> 00:34:40.156 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's it, isn't it?</c.bg_transparent>

592
00:34:41.496 --> 00:34:43.338 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's why you won't even defend yourself.</c.bg_transparent>

593
00:34:49.194 --> 00:34:52.136 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>There are worse things</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>than an illicit love affair.</c.bg_transparent>

594
00:34:52.955 --> 00:34:54.454 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Curzon didn't murder anybody.</c.bg_transparent>

595
00:34:54.454 --> 00:34:56.094 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He didn't commit treason.</c.bg_transparent>

596
00:34:58.142 --> 00:35:02.014 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Are you really willing to commit suicide</c.bg_transparent>
