597
00:35:02.330 --> 00:35:03.431 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That is what you're doing, you know.</c.bg_transparent>

598
00:35:08.029 --> 00:35:09.199 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>My God, Dax.</c.bg_transparent>

599
00:35:09.668 --> 00:35:11.630 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Young Tandro... That wouldn't be your son?</c.bg_transparent>

600
00:35:12.493 --> 00:35:14.307 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You have an overactive imagination,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Benjamin.</c.bg_transparent>

601
00:35:15.047 --> 00:35:17.109 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Then what is it that's holding you back?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Help me.</c.bg_transparent>

602
00:35:19.486 --> 00:35:20.485 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( grunting )</c.bg_transparent>

603
00:35:20.485 --> 00:35:22.005 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Damn it, if you were still a man...</c.bg_transparent>

604
00:35:24.044 --> 00:35:24.963 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( bangs wall )</c.bg_transparent>

605
00:35:28.443 --> 00:35:30.562 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I see your temper hasn't improved.</c.bg_transparent>

606
00:35:30.642 --> 00:35:32.780 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Don't talk to me about my temper.</c.bg_transparent>

607
00:35:32.825 --> 00:35:33.773 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Curzon always warned you about it.</c.bg_transparent>

608
00:35:34.061 --> 00:35:35.742 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're not going to get me off track here.</c.bg_transparent>

609
00:35:37.860 --> 00:35:41.903 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Do you remember that Argosian Lieutenant</c.bg_transparent>
