610
00:35:44.001 --> 00:35:46.577 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( both laughing )</c.bg_transparent>

611
00:35:47.868 --> 00:35:50.478 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>And you knocked me down with a right cross</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>before I could kill him.</c.bg_transparent>

612
00:35:52.575 --> 00:35:54.817 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I still have a little scar here</c.bg_transparent>
