613
00:35:58.733 --> 00:36:02.892 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I tried on that ring after Curzon died.</c.bg_transparent>

614
00:36:04.372 --> 00:36:06.891 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It just slipped off my finger.</c.bg_transparent>

615
00:36:09.251 --> 00:36:12.393 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If you don't help me, old man,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>they're going to take you</c.bg_transparent>

616
00:36:13.389 --> 00:36:15.611 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>because I don't know any more arguments.</c.bg_transparent>

617
00:36:18.008 --> 00:36:19.269 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Then allow it to happen.</c.bg_transparent>

618
00:36:20.307 --> 00:36:23.850 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It is my obligation to protect the lives</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of those in my command.</c.bg_transparent>

619
00:36:24.086 --> 00:36:25.706 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You ought to know that,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>you taught it to me.</c.bg_transparent>

620
00:36:27.985 --> 00:36:29.245 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That was Curzon.</c.bg_transparent>

621
00:36:30.665 --> 00:36:32.086 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'll stop trying to protect you</c.bg_transparent>

622
00:36:32.086 --> 00:36:34.976 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>the minute you tell me Curzon was guilty</c.bg_transparent>
