630
00:36:58.775 --> 00:37:02.498 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I can tell you... that he did love her</c.bg_transparent>

631
00:37:03.814 --> 00:37:05.035 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>for whatever that's worth.</c.bg_transparent>

632
00:37:06.324 --> 00:37:07.545 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Enough to kill her husband?</c.bg_transparent>

633
00:37:10.072 --> 00:37:11.233 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>So you are questioning?</c.bg_transparent>

634
00:37:12.571 --> 00:37:13.432 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What else can I do?</c.bg_transparent>

635
00:37:16.090 --> 00:37:18.289 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Nothing, Benjamin.</c.bg_transparent>

636
00:37:18.370 --> 00:37:20.129 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Nothing at all.</c.bg_transparent>

637
00:37:35.704 --> 00:37:39.887 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Lieutenant Dax, you are either</c.bg_transparent>
