638
00:37:40.063 --> 00:37:42.845 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>or you're about the same age</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>as my great-granddaughter.</c.bg_transparent>

639
00:37:44.043 --> 00:37:46.004 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>At first,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I wondered which of those you were.</c.bg_transparent>

640
00:37:46.582 --> 00:37:50.825 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Now, I am bothered</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>by the likelihood that you may be both.</c.bg_transparent>

641
00:37:54.219 --> 00:37:56.218 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Let's finish this, Commander.</c.bg_transparent>

642
00:37:57.618 --> 00:38:02.376 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>At what age did the host, Jadzia</c.bg_transparent>
