00:38:08.595 --> 00:38:09.776 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>among potential hosts?</c.bg_transparent>

646
00:38:10.274 --> 00:38:12.476 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
