653
00:38:26.573 --> 00:38:27.693 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yes.</c.bg_transparent>

654
00:38:27.773 --> 00:38:32.651 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>And the young Jadzia excelled in those</c.bg_transparent>
