00:38:32.651 --> 00:38:33.784 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>of psychological stability.</c.bg_transparent>

656
00:38:35.964 --> 00:38:36.531 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yes.</c.bg_transparent>

657
00:38:37.466 --> 00:38:41.069 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If you can remember other things,</c.bg_transparent>
