00:39:01.680 --> 00:39:03.119 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>All of them.</c.bg_transparent>

663
00:39:03.200 --> 00:39:05.079 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
