664
00:39:06.079 --> 00:39:07.478 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>As Jadzia.</c.bg_transparent>

665
00:39:07.478 --> 00:39:07.843 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Alone.</c.bg_transparent>

666
00:39:10.977 --> 00:39:13.878 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>This brilliant and independent</c.bg_transparent>
