687
00:40:16.019 --> 00:40:17.739 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Mother, what are you talking about?</c.bg_transparent>

688
00:40:19.417 --> 00:40:20.497 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Madam Arbiter,</c.bg_transparent>

689
