698
00:41:23.419 --> 00:41:25.741 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It was kind of you</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to try and protect me...</c.bg_transparent>

699
00:41:27.555 --> 00:41:28.856 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
